story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0100: We finally managed to sneak into their hideout!
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0200: It was a really close one... We had to battle a lot.
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0400: Hey! This is as far as you go!
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0600: We’ll win, no matter how many of them come!
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0700:
Why can’t we beat them?! They should be tired
by now!
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_0800: You’re just getting started, aren’t you, Hilda?
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_1200: That’s true... We came all this way.
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_1300: We don’t have time to wait around!
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_1500:
Her positive attitude is giving strength to everyone
around her...
story_teamplasma_02_04000/2401_1001_1600:
So this is what can be achieved through the bonds
of friendship!
